Layer                   Teknologi                               Fungsi
Frontend        React + Vite (Streamlit Template)   UI Map, event listener, rendering
Map Engine      Leaflet + Leaflet-Draw              Rendering peta, klik, gambar polygon
Geospatial      toGeoJSON() (JS) ↔ geopandas (Python)   Format data spasial standar
Backend         Streamlit st.components.v1              Bridge JS ↔ Python
State/Perf      st.session_state + @st.fragment         Isolasi rerun, cache model
Communication   Streamlit.setComponentValue()           Kirim event/data JS → Python


🔁 Alur Data (Bidirectional)
[JS: Click/Draw] → Streamlit.setComponentValue({type, payload}) 
       ↓
[Python: st.components] → return dict ke variabel Python
       ↓
[Python: st.session_state] → trigger prediction (isolated via @st.fragment)
       ↓
[Python: Model + Geopandas] → hasil prediksi
       ↓
[Python → JS] → props.args / Streamlit.renderData() → render overlay di peta


Frontend Implementation (React + Leaflet)
import React, { useEffect, useRef } from 'react';
import L from 'leaflet';
import 'leaflet-draw';
import 'leaflet/dist/leaflet.css';
import 'leaflet-draw/dist/leaflet.draw.css';
import { Streamlit, ComponentProps } from 'streamlit-component-lib';

// Fix ikon default Leaflet di React/Vite
delete (L.Icon.Default.prototype as any)._getIconUrl;
L.Icon.Default.mergeOptions({
  iconRetinaUrl: 'https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/images/marker-icon-2x.png',
  iconUrl: 'https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/images/marker-icon.png',
  shadowUrl: 'https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/images/marker-shadow.png',
});

export function InteractiveMap(props: ComponentProps) {
  const mapRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);
  const mapInstance = useRef<L.Map | null>(null);
  const drawnItems = useRef<L.FeatureGroup | null>(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (!mapRef.current || mapInstance.current) return;

    // Inisialisasi peta
    mapInstance.current = L.map(mapRef.current).setView([-6.175, 106.827], 12);
    L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {
      attribution: '© OpenStreetMap'
    }).addTo(mapInstance.current);

    // Layer untuk AOI
    drawnItems.current = new L.FeatureGroup();
    mapInstance.current.addLayer(drawnItems.current);

    // Kontrol Draw (hanya Polygon)
    const drawControl = new L.Control.Draw({
      draw: { polygon: true, rectangle: false, circle: false, marker: false, polyline: false },
      edit: { featureGroup: drawnItems.current }
    });
    mapInstance.current.addControl(drawControl);

    // Event: Click
    mapInstance.current.on('click', (e: L.LeafletMouseEvent) => {
      Streamlit.setComponentValue({
        type: 'click',
        lat: e.latlng.lat,
        lng: e.latlng.lng,
        timestamp: Date.now()
      });
    });

    // Event: Draw Created
    mapInstance.current.on(L.Draw.Event.CREATED, (e: any) => {
      const layer = e.layer;
      drawnItems.current?.addLayer(layer);
      
      Streamlit.setComponentValue({
        type: 'aoi',
        geometry: layer.toGeoJSON(),
        timestamp: Date.now()
      });
    });

    // Event: Draw Edited/Deleted
    mapInstance.current.on(L.Draw.Event.EDITED, (e: any) => {
      const layers = e.layers;
      const updatedGeoJSONs = [];
      layers.eachLayer((layer: L.Layer) => {
        updatedGeoJSONs.push((layer as L.Polygon).toGeoJSON());
      });
      Streamlit.setComponentValue({
        type: 'aoi_updated',
        geometries: updatedGeoJSONs,
        timestamp: Date.now()
      });
    });

    Streamlit.setComponentReady();
  }, []);

  // Terima data dari Python (misal: hasil prediksi untuk di-render)
  useEffect(() => {
    if (props.args.predictionOverlay && mapInstance.current && drawnItems.current) {
      // Hapus overlay lama
      drawnItems.current.clearLayers();
      // Render GeoJSON baru
      L.geoJSON(props.args.predictionOverlay).addTo(drawnItems.current);
      mapInstance.current.fitBounds(drawnItems.current.getBounds());
    }
  }, [props.args]);

  return <div ref={mapRef} style={{ width: '100%', height: props.args.height || 600 }} />;
}

Backend Integration (Streamlit Python)
import streamlit as st
import streamlit.components.v1 as components
import geopandas as gpd
from shapely.geometry import Point, shape
import numpy as np

# 1. Declare component (path ke folder build frontend)
InteractiveMap = components.declare_component("interactive_map", path="frontend/build")

# 2. Load model sekali saja (cache resource)
@st.cache_resource
def load_model():
    # Ganti dengan model kamu (sklearn, pytorch, tensorflow, dll)
    return {"dummy": lambda x, y: np.random.rand()}

model = load_model()

# 3. Inisialisasi session state
if "map_output" not in st.session_state:
    st.session_state.map_output = None
if "prediction_result" not in st.session_state:
    st.session_state.prediction_result = None
if "aoi_geojson" not in st.session_state:
    st.session_state.aoi_geojson = None

# 4. Render komponen
st.header("🌍 Interactive Prediction Map")
map_output = InteractiveMap(
    height=600,
    predictionOverlay=st.session_state.prediction_result
)

# 5. Tangani event dari JS
if map_output and map_output.get("type") in ["click", "aoi", "aoi_updated"]:
    st.session_state.map_output = map_output
    trigger_prediction(map_output)

# 6. Fragment untuk isolasi rerun (hanya bagian ini yang rerun)
@st.fragment
def trigger_prediction(data):
    with st.spinner("🔍 Predicting..."):
        if data["type"] == "click":
            lat, lon = data["lat"], data["lng"]
            pred = model["dummy"](lat, lon)
            st.success(f"📍 Single Click: ({lat:.4f}, {lon:.4f}) → Prediction: {pred:.3f}")
            
        elif data["type"] in ["aoi", "aoi_updated"]:
            geo = data.get("geometry") or data["geometries"][0]
            polygon = shape(geo["geometry"])
            gdf = gpd.GeoDataFrame({"geometry": [polygon]}, crs="EPSG:4326")
            
            # Contoh: buat grid 50x50m di dalam polygon
            grid = gdf.iloc[0].geometry.buffer(0).bounds
            xs = np.linspace(grid[0], grid[2], 20)
            ys = np.linspace(grid[1], grid[3], 20)
            points = [Point(x, y) for x in xs for y in ys if gdf.contains(Point(x, y)).any()]
            
            preds = [model["dummy"](p.y, p.x) for p in points]
            
            # Format balik ke GeoJSON untuk dikirim ke JS
            features = [{
                "type": "Feature",
                "geometry": {"type": "Point", "coordinates": [p.x, p.y]},
                "properties": {"prediction": float(p)}
            } for p, pred in zip(points, preds)]
            
            st.session_state.prediction_result = {
                "type": "FeatureCollection",
                "features": features
            }
            st.success(f"📐 AOI Batch: {len(points)} points predicted")


Teknik Komunikasi & Event Handling

Teknik                                          Penjelasan
Streamlit.setComponentValue()              Kirim payload JS → Python. Hanya trigger 1x per event.
props.args                                 Kirim data Python → JS. Update UI tanpa reload.
@st.fragment                        Isolasi rerun. Hanya fragment yang rerun, tidak mengganggu sidebar/widget lain.
timestamp field                     Hindari duplicate trigger akibat Streamlit double-render. Cek if data.get("timestamp") != last_ts.
GeoJSON standar                     Leaflet toGeoJSON() menghasilkan RFC 7946. Langsung kompatibel dengan geopandas.from_features().

Integrasi Model & Batch Prediction
Strategi AOI Batch:
    1. Parse GeoJSON → shapely.geometry.shape()
    2.Validasi CRS (EPSG:4326)
    3.Generate grid/raster di dalam polygon (geopandas.clip + numpy.meshgrid)
    4.Vectorized prediction (model.predict(X_batch))
    5.Convert hasil ke GeoJSON FeatureCollection
    6.Kirim balik ke JS via predictionOverlay props
    7.Render sebagai heatmap/marker cluster di Leaflet

Optimasi Data Science:
   - Gunakan @st.cache_resource untuk model & tokenizer/encoder
   - Precompute features jika memungkinkan
   - Batasi grid resolution (misal 50m atau 100m) agar tidak OOM
   - Gunakan geopandas.sjoin jika prediksi berbasis zone/shapefile existing

Best Practices & Troubleshooting
Map hilang state setelah rerun
----Pindahkan inisialisasi map ke useEffect([]) dengan dependency kosong. Gunakan Streamlit.setComponentReady()
Payload terlalu besar
----Chunk GeoJSON, gunakan precision: 4 di JS, atau kirim hanya bounding box + grid count
Model predict lambat
----Gunakan @st.cache_data untuk feature engineering, @st.cache_resource untuk model, tampilkan st.progress
Leaflet icon broken
----Gunakan CDN atau bundle ikon secara manual di vite.config.ts
Double trigger event
----Tambah timestamp atau event_id di JS, filter di Python dengan st.session_state.last_event_id